{"tid":2292900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法國啲人好鐘意講「冇呀」，但明明就有","createTime":"2020-11-20T00:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T01:56:56.000Z","uid":154478,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2da1607a4cba5a49ca870ae5bfbfdd31359a9ab2","tid":2292900,"uid":154478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇留意，啲人好習慣係唔係都答左「冇呀」先。<br />\n例子：<br />\nA: 你琴日去左邊玩？<br />\nB: 冇呀，去左唱k<br />\n明明就有，就係去左唱k，點解要答左「冇呀」先？<br />\n<br />\n正評：每次聽到都覺得好un耳<br />\n負評：我都係咁，唔覺得有問題"},{"pid":"ab17fec9f16fbc570cc4affed6f93c4d420e16bd","tid":2292900,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"冇呀係代表冇嘢特別<br />\n例如你問去邊玩<br />\n咁唱K只係普通活動，唔算特別去玩，所以咪話冇呀"},{"pid":"1a80bbce91a9d48c4da9f1b2dc5eba8b1704cdc8","tid":2292900,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"有冇偷睇我d牌？"},{"pid":"c0b752f17ffdc05b53f3eb21c2b76fc9e883bb5e","tid":2292900,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:57:55.000Z","msg":"冇呀=冇咩特別呀"},{"pid":"518f5cb9d636f9fc605154133b76b14905eafb65","tid":2292900,"uid":152663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智fact checked"},{"pid":"dc0d83765c53f5cf73d428690712594695309ac1","tid":2292900,"uid":24688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"本身唔想你知，拖下時間諗點講咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62446151c481b70a5e653d3a3ab405e078bfa8fd","tid":2292900,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"入黎之前仲以為樓主係講明明望住佢做咗衰嘢，但對方都可以話冇呀果種<br />\n<br />\n我都係出番去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae98639b2a50711195f3562bbab180270dbdd90","tid":2292900,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"因為呀B對唱k好撚認